  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a cazuela over medium-high heat.",
    "Add onion, garlic, and ginger; cook, stirring occasionally, until onion is lightly browned, about 8 minutes.",
    "Add tomatoes, garam masala, cumin, turmeric, salt, and black pepper; cook, stirring occasionally, for 2 minutes.",
    "Add anchovy fillets and cook, stirring occasionally, for 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in lime juice and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Reduce heat to medium-low and simmer, uncovered, for 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in chopped cilantro and mint; cook for 1 minute.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional cilantro and lime wedges.",
    "Serve with rice or naan for a filling meal."
